        <div class="review-polaroid"><div class="review-polaroid-tape"></div><div class="review-polaroid-photo"><div class="review-polaroid-grain"></div><div class="review-polaroid-burn"></div><div class="review-polaroid-glow"></div><div class="review-polaroid-glow2"></div><div class="review-polaroid-sheen"></div><div class="review-polaroid-photo-inner"><span class="review-polaroid-stars">★★★★★</span><p class="review-polaroid-text">"Hands down, the best barbershop I've ever been to. Always spotless, welcoming atmosphere, and staff that is incredibly skilled and professional."</p></div></div><div class="review-polaroid-caption"><div class="review-polaroid-name">Nabil Kendri</div><div class="review-polaroid-source">Verified Google Review</div></div><div class="review-polaroid-bottom-edge"></div></div>

